1.1.name: wordpress/spoiler-block
1.1.description:
This plugin create a button in your Wordpress editor to set some parts of your posts as spoilers. These parts show a blocked content to your visitors, then must click in these blocks to show the original content.

Translators

  • Brazilian (pt_BR) - Brunno dos Santos
  • Romanian (ro) - Alexander Ovsov
